Fantastic Four's Kate Mara and Jamie Bell Are Not Hiding Their Romance Anymore—See Them Pack on the PDA 
E online Friday 23rd October, 2015 
romance rumors resurfaced.Well, the guessing game is officially over.Throwing caution to the wind, Mara, 32, and Bell, 29, kissed on a street corner in New York City's Soho neighborhood Thursday. And as the saying goes, a picture is worth a thousand words. Prior to getting together this year, Bell had been single for over a year after...
